		                  the holy Christian Church,<br/>
		                       the communion of saints,<br/>
		                  the forgiveness of sins,<br/>
		                  the resurrection of the body,<br/>
		                  and the life everlasting. Amen.<br/>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		
	</div>
</div>
</body>",
